      "end": 160.72,
      "text": "Maybe cause all I could do then was stare at the floor"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.72,
      "end": 164.48,
      "text": "어쩌면 cause all I could do then"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.48,
      "end": 167.88,
      "text": "그 당시에 그때 내가 할 수 있었던 건 그저"
